data.description: Easy one level floor plan in 55+ community with a quiet park like setting. Spacious living room with brick corner fireplace, beautiful original hardwood floors throughout, large bedrooms and closets, and a convenient laundry/storage room. Pull down stairs gives access to even more plentiful attic storage above. Covered patio with small open, sunny garden area to enjoy a bit of gardening. 2 Deeded parking spaces, one under the carport and an additional uncovered parking space. Unit is clean and ready to move in and could be updated according to your needs, taste and budget. Recent updates include: new interior paint, new floors in kitchen, bathroom and utility room, plumbing updates in utility room, bathroom and kitchen, new electrical outlets and lighting, new bathroom vanity, sink and faucet, and new kitchen faucet. Community amenities include private pool, clubhouse/party room with kitchen, library, ample guest parking. All this with reasonable HOA fees!  Welcome home! [Home Energy Score = 6. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10214857]
